graph TD
    subgraph "Local Development"
        Dev[Developer] --> Git[Git Push]
    end

    subgraph "CI/CD (GitHub Actions)"
        Git --> GHA[Deploy Workflow]
        GHA --> Test[Automated Tests: Jest/Vitest]
        Test --> WIF[OIDC / WIF Auth]
        WIF --> TF[Terraform Apply]
        TF --> CB[Cloud Build]
    end

    subgraph "GCP Staging Environment"
        CB --> GCR[Artifact Registry]
        GCR --> CR[Cloud Run: Server]
        TF --> FS[Firestore: Native]
        TF --> SM[Secret Manager]
        GHA --> FH[Firebase Hosting: Web]
    end

    subgraph "Identity & Access"
        WIF -.-> |Impersonates| GSA[github-deployer]
        CR -.-> |Identity| SSA[task-manager-server]
        SSA --> |roles/datastore.user| FS
        SSA --> |roles/secretmanager.secretAccessor| SM
    end

    FH --> |/api/* Rewrites| CR
